<P>
Dance Appointments: A new president and chief executive officer has come on 
board at Dance Gallery, the new arts complex conceived by Bella Lewitzky to be 
built in the heart of Los Angeles at California Plaza. Martin I. Kagan last 
served as executive director of Washington's OPERA America, the service 
organization of professional opera companies in North America and abroad. He 
has also managed the Dennis Wayne Dancers, the Anna Wyman Dance Theatre and 
Jacob's Pillow Dance Festival. CLAUDIA PUIG 
