Agence France-Presse; Photo, Views of Bernstein: Leonard Bernstein's last 
conducting appearance, above, at Tanglewood, Mass., on Aug. 19. 1990 ALAN 
SOLOMON; Photo, Bernstein, left, as he appeared at the Hollywood Bowl in 1982, 
and guiding the Los Angeles Philharmonic, below, also in 1982. Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, (Southland Edition) Leonard Bernstein in 1988. STEVE J. SHERMAN 
</P>
