<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
SCUBA DIVING; DIVING ACCIDENTS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; MISSING PERSONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA101590-0104 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 292874 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 15, 1990, Monday, Ventura County Edition 
</P>
